data.title: Video Illinois governor responds to Trump's call to jail Democratic leaders
data.text: Illinois governor responds to Trump's call to jail Democratic leaders Illinois Gov. JB Pritzker responded after President Donald Trump called for his jailing in a social media post claiming Pritzker and Chicago Mayor Brandon Johnson have failed to protect ICE officers.
data.summary:
